  "caveats": [
    "The sandbox has curl/HTTP but not PageSpeed Insights, the Rich Results Test, Search Console, Screaming Frog, or Ahrefs — so Core Web Vitals (field data), JavaScript-rendered schema, indexation coverage, and backlinks are flagged 'requires external tool', not guessed. This is a thorough STATIC audit (robots/sitemaps, titles/meta/H1s, canonicals, hreflang, internal links, alt text, HTTPS).",
    "Audits a live site, so findings reflect the site as fetched on the run date and can change as the site changes."
  ],

